    <h3>Turning spreadsheets into reality</h3>
    <p>If you have a copy of Adobe Illustrator, you can apply these changes to the character sheets directly.</p>
    <p>Get a copy of the entire project using Git, and make sure your translation file is saved as CSV, using Unicode format, with comma delimiters.
